'Janny' gets on his skates to help pupils at a Newton Mearns school perform Uptown FunkA school 'janny' has got on in his skates to help pupils perform Uptown Funk in a new viral video.The version of Uptown Funk is the latest to hit the web from a Scottish school.It features pupils with additional support needs who attend Isobel Mair School in Newton Mearns.One of the teachers even use sign language though parts of the song.The video was filmed to say farewell to the 6th year leavers.